How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

2 out of 5 stars
The batter wont stay charged.
I love this watch other than the batter will not stay charged. And this is the second one! My first one came fully charged. And lasted 4 days on that charge. Then I charged it and after that it wouldnt even last a full 12 hours! This watch was only at half charge when I got it. So I charged it right away before using it. I used it for my walk yesterday morning 12/28/24 and this morning it is dead 12/29/24. I cant wear it all day as it irritates my skin but I use it everytime I walk as its the most accurate tracker I have. Im just really disappointed that it doesnt stay charged for more then 8-12hrs.
